column3: “So this strain hits smoooooth. The smell is woody, deep, herby and with your typical OG smell". As I said
column5: and the exhale tastes pretty good too. I got a nice and deep body high too. I fell asleep pretty quick as well. Try this out!”"

column3: “nice relaxing high, great for chilling with your squad, some fifa, COD and more. nice taste with a great burn.”

“The high isn't very prominent, I have to smoke a lot, probably 2 1/2 bowls to myself to get where I'd like to be and maintain my high. Large buds, not very dense, not super sticky, feels dry. Once I get to my HP the high is awesome though, I'd recommend it, but definitely not my first choice.”
“Good for evening chill, play some games, party with squad.”
